      \item Jones, M.\ B., Bradley, J., \& Sakimura, N.\ (2015). \textit{JSON Web Token (JWT)}. RFC 7519. IETF.
      \item Provos, N., \& Mazieres, D.\ (1999). \textit{A Future-Adaptable Password Scheme}. USENIX Annual Technical Conference.
